SUMMARY:Flower Arranging Class with Sweet Serendipity
DESCRIPTION:Grab a friend and learn the basics of floral design with local NC blooms! Guided instruction and supplies will be provided.\nBe creative\, arrange something beautiful\, and make a mess. Don’t worry\, I’ll clean it up!\nGrab a friend\, get lucky\, and learn the basics of floral design with beautiful blooms atHoneygirl Meadery! This class will have bright flowers\, beautiful greenery\, and lucky add-ons such as gold coins\, glittery shamrocks\, vibrant ribbon\, and more.\nGuided instruction will teach you all the tips and tricks you need to make a beautiful arrangement to bring home with you.\nTicket prices include containers and all floral supplies. Design tools are provided. All plants are animal safe unless otherwise stated.
URL:https://downtowndurham.com/event/flower-arranging-class-with-sweet-serendipity/
