SUMMARY:Durham St. Patrick's Day Treasure Hunt - Walking Team Scavenger Hunt!
DESCRIPTION:Guests will meet at Crank Arm Brewing Co. (620 Fernway Ave.\, Durham\, NC 27701) and then depart with their treasure map on a walking team scavenger hunt where they will use their minds and feet to follow St. Patrick’s Day themed clues\, solve puzzles\, and crack codes to find and unlock the treasure chest for a grand prize! \nThe hunt involves walking a up to 2.0 miles in total and will take place rain or shine\, so long as the weather does not become dangerous. The hunt typically takes about 60 minutes to complete. \nChildren under 10 years old are welcome to participate for free with the purchase of an Adult ticket.
URL:https://downtowndurham.com/event/durham-st-patricks-day-treasure-hunt-walking-team-scavenger-hunt-2/
