DESCRIPTION:Celebrate St. Paddy’s with LIVE Irish music and help support Women’s Voices Chorus! \nFeaturing an Irish instrumental jam session led by Eileen Regan and the High Strung Sessioners\, as well as a singalong led by members of Women’s Voices Chorus! \nBONUS: We’ll be donating 10% of sales on select beers to WVC. \nBring your friends and enjoy a festive afternoon of music! \n 
