SUMMARY:The Sunday Set on the Roof
DESCRIPTION:Consider this your invitation back. The Sunday Set is returning to the Roof for its second season. Kick it off with us Sunday\, March 15th\, from 4 to 10 PM with $2 oysters\, a $10 build-your-own spritz bar\, DJ set with Gemynii from 5 to 8 PM\, and skyline views that never get old. \nThe Sunday Set Keychain\nOn opening day\, Sunday\, March 15\, the first 50 guests to arrive will receive a custom Sunday Set keychain that comes with perks all season long. Flash it on the Roof any Sunday through October and your Snack Board is on us. \nWhat’s on the Snack Board: veggie crudité\, Old Bay chips with house-made ranch\, seasonal popcorn\, roasted nuts. $18 value\, complimentary every Sunday you’re here with your Sunday Set keychain.
URL:https://downtowndurham.com/event/the-sunday-set-on-the-roof/
