SUMMARY:Trivia Night at Fizzwerks
DESCRIPTION:Make Mondays something to look forward to! Join us every Monday at 7:00 PM for Trivia Night with Jesse\, featuring a rotating mix of pop culture\, sports\, food & drink\, and general knowledge questions. It is a a fun\, fast-paced trivia night with gift card prizes and a $10 Pierogies + Pint special. Free to play and always a good time. Bring a team or come solo — all are welcome. Seating is first come\, first served\, so arrive early to grab a table and a pint.
