DESCRIPTION:Durham’s Alley Twenty Six is now offering $1.50 raw oyster special from 4-5 p.m. Tuesdays-Fridays. A selection of oysters are sourced from North Carolina and often Canada\, Virginia or elsewhere along the East Coast and served with cocktail sauce\, Mignonette sauce and lemon. Bar seats are available first come\, first serve or make a reservation at alleytwentysix.com.
